rows.label: qst201402_msg0002
rows.name: I've run out of things to say...

rows.label: qst201402_msg0003
rows.name:
It seems we won't settle
this unless we both polish
our conversation skills.

rows.label: qst201402_msg0005
rows.name:
Let's continue this another
day. Be fully prepared for it!

rows.label: qst201402_msg0006
rows.name: Agreed! We'll settle it next time!

rows.label: qst201402_msg0103
rows.name:
Two hours just flew by.
This is getting fun!

rows.label: qst201402_msg0104
rows.name: Now then, the next topic is...

rows.label: qst201402_msg0105
rows.name:
It's almost a new day, and we
still haven't run out of topics!

rows.label: qst201402_msg0107
rows.name: Hmm, what should I talk about next?

rows.label: qst201402_msg0108
rows.name:
It's already 3 AM, but
we're still going strong!

rows.label: qst201402_msg0109
rows.name:
Ugh, my ears are getting tired...
But I can't back down here.

rows.label: qst201402_msg0110
rows.name:
It's almost dawn. Any interesting
stories to wake me up...

rows.label: qst201402_msg0111
rows.name:
I'm at my limit... No,
no, I can't lose here!

rows.label: qst201402_msg0201
rows.name: Come on, let's settle this for good!

rows.label: qst201402_msg0202
rows.name:
We could start over, but Hikari
would get bored, so let's pick
up where we left off.
